{"tid":1422002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"郊遊野餐必備餐單","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T12:04:04.000Z","uid":142883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"38e42ce17d81779cce41360d9e9fcf9fa281ef23","tid":1422002,"uid":142883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:30:57.000Z","msg":"相信大家最近係各區郊遊野餐食胡椒同食蛋都食都悶喇，我推介大家食下其他更有營養嘅食品平衡下。<br />\n呢樣野就係瑞典嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">鯡魚罐頭</span></span>喇，雖然佢<span style=\"color: red;\">氣味濃烈</span>，但佢有個罐保護，浸味冇咁容易漏出嚟。但小心，因為佢係發酵食物，只要受到好似投擲或者彈弓大力嘅碰撞，佢就會爆開，啲汁會噴到周圍都係，用水炮車都<span style=\"color: red;\">好難清潔</span>架喇。<br />\n而家ebay都有得賣，有興趣郊遊嘅人可以買嚟自己食又得，請其他人食都得。但千祈唔好比狗之類嘅動物食呀，佢地會怕臭，仲會整到啲毛，最大鑊係帶返入狗屋，好難洗嫁。<br />\n如果大家仲有咩郊遊嘅食物建議，可以係下面留言。"},{"pid":"0d4f1966c96e9b8cf5358793a903f1c596dd4aaa","tid":1422002,"uid":142883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:32:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fabc691cef822c8857349fda77dfcc1502ac6f9a","tid":1422002,"uid":25085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"可唔可以配法國麵包食"},{"pid":"89a704e35fa504dd27e1f1cadc4c4a8ee684f380","tid":1422002,"uid":142883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fabc691cef822c8857349fda77dfcc1502ac6f9a","tid":1422002,"uid":25085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"可唔可以配法國麵包食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:34:56.000Z","msg":"當然可以啦，放左一星期嘅法包又硬又濃郁，一定適合，都係句：唔好比狗食呀。"},{"pid":"06cb50891c7b67fce74227e554887856b01c138d","tid":1422002,"uid":142883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:35:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f48924b7fa38b4602df033fe3b2f6899eeac2c7f","tid":1422002,"uid":142883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5437ce92bb99cf4639816ec09232e75777fbb909","tid":1422002,"uid":58950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:15:51.000Z","msg":"有無得整個郊遊食物清單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c4619b29e4e9eed1112b54d855fff190697071","tid":1422002,"uid":25085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}